WEBVTT

00:40.457 --> 00:43.710
ALL CHARACTERS, PLACES, GROUPS, AND
ORGANIZATIONS IN THIS WORK ARE FICTITIOUS

00:43.793 --> 00:46.379
SCENES WITH ANIMALS ARE STAGED
ACCORDING TO ANIMAL WELFARE GUIDELINES

00:51.301 --> 00:52.343
Sit.

00:53.803 --> 00:54.679
Okay.

01:09.444 --> 01:10.528
Hey!

01:11.029 --> 01:12.072
Sit.

01:29.005 --> 01:30.298
Why did you do it?

01:40.809 --> 01:42.310
Answer me.

01:44.437 --> 01:46.940
Why did you kill Bom's grandma?

01:48.066 --> 01:50.527
What did she do wrong?

01:55.031 --> 01:56.741
Why did you kill her?

02:03.915 --> 02:04.999
Grandma…

02:06.709 --> 02:07.752
Grandma…

02:10.630 --> 02:11.673
Grandma.

02:13.216 --> 02:14.342
Grandma.

02:15.009 --> 02:17.262
-Grandma is in danger!
-Hey, stop it!

02:20.598 --> 02:22.100
Grandma is hurt!

02:22.684 --> 02:24.144
Run!

02:24.727 --> 02:26.396
Run away!

02:26.479 --> 02:29.190
-Can you give me a hand here?
-Grandma, run away!

02:29.274 --> 02:31.151
-Grandma, danger!
-Drag him out.

02:31.234 --> 02:33.862
-She's in danger!
-Let's go.

02:38.408 --> 02:40.451
TICKET
DESTINATION: SEOUL

02:41.661 --> 02:43.246
We have four seats left for Seoul.

02:43.746 --> 02:45.123
Are there any more passengers?

03:01.681 --> 03:04.350
SEON-A BILLIARD CLUB

03:33.379 --> 03:34.422
Seon-a!

03:39.302 --> 03:40.678
SEON-A BILLIARD CLUB

03:41.262 --> 03:42.263
Seon-a.

03:44.098 --> 03:45.475
Where are you?

03:46.559 --> 03:47.769
I'm here, Mom.

03:48.728 --> 03:49.812
Mom.

03:50.647 --> 03:51.981
Mom!

03:54.525 --> 03:55.568
Mom.

04:28.434 --> 04:29.560
Dae-bum.

05:20.069 --> 05:21.612
It's been rough, right?

06:02.528 --> 06:03.571
Who is it?

06:05.615 --> 06:06.824
Who is it?

06:16.334 --> 06:17.710
What are you doing here?

06:18.628 --> 06:19.921
Have you been well?

06:22.590 --> 06:23.466
Yes.

06:24.258 --> 06:26.177
But what brings you here?

06:27.929 --> 06:29.222
I missed you.

06:35.937 --> 06:37.522
Wait out here for a second.

06:37.605 --> 06:38.481
Bom.

06:40.608 --> 06:43.111
Can I go into your house too?

06:44.320 --> 06:45.363
What?

06:45.905 --> 06:48.032
I'm sure Yeo-reum has been to your house

06:49.158 --> 06:51.828
and Dae-ho as well.

06:54.539 --> 06:56.124
Please let me in as well.

07:06.717 --> 07:09.178
Way to visit out of the blue.

07:09.262 --> 07:10.263
Sorry.

07:11.848 --> 07:13.015
Let's go out.

07:13.099 --> 07:14.142
Why?

07:14.225 --> 07:16.144
You've seen the house now. Get up.

07:16.644 --> 07:17.854
Can't we stay a little longer?

07:17.937 --> 07:18.980
No.

07:22.733 --> 07:24.360
I'm going to practice too.

07:26.946 --> 07:28.948
I want to know how you feel,

07:30.450 --> 07:34.162
and I want to do everything for you
without being told what to do.

07:38.332 --> 07:40.084
You can't.

07:40.168 --> 07:42.795
Why not? I can.

07:44.046 --> 07:45.756
I'll come over often.

07:45.840 --> 07:47.175
I'll also spend more time

07:47.258 --> 07:49.719
-with your family and neighbors--
-But you're Heo Jae-hun.

07:56.184 --> 07:57.435
That's all I need.

07:59.729 --> 08:03.232
I want you to stay clumsy and slow-witted.

08:08.571 --> 08:10.573
So, do you want water or anything?

08:11.949 --> 08:12.950
No.

08:13.743 --> 08:14.869
Then…

08:15.703 --> 08:18.289
can I try the tomatoes over there?

08:19.457 --> 08:20.917
When did you spot those?

08:21.000 --> 08:21.918
Come here.

08:55.660 --> 08:58.371
The blankets are ready.

08:59.121 --> 09:00.331
And…

09:02.291 --> 09:05.169
there's some water
and some apples in the fridge.

09:06.379 --> 09:08.089
You can have that.

09:08.172 --> 09:09.215
Okay.

09:09.298 --> 09:10.716
Then I'll get going.

09:12.260 --> 09:13.719
Where are you going?

09:13.803 --> 09:15.096
I'm going to the library.

09:16.222 --> 09:17.890
-At this hour?
-Yes.

09:18.641 --> 09:19.934
That's ridiculous.

09:20.518 --> 09:21.435
I…

09:21.519 --> 09:23.729
will sleep in the living room.

09:23.813 --> 09:25.398
You can sleep in the room.

09:25.481 --> 09:28.484
No, it's fine. I don't think
you'd be comfortable if I stayed.

09:28.568 --> 09:29.819
-No.
-Rest up then.

09:29.902 --> 09:30.861
Then I'll go out.

09:30.945 --> 09:33.239
-No.
-It's fine. I'll go to the library.

09:33.322 --> 09:35.992
I can't stay in your house all alone.

09:36.075 --> 09:38.703
-I'll go.
-Yeo-reum, please wait.

09:39.620 --> 09:40.705
Gosh.

09:45.793 --> 09:46.711
Ha-neul.

09:48.296 --> 09:49.338
Ha-neul.

09:51.674 --> 09:53.009
Hey, you're back.

09:53.092 --> 09:54.885
You didn't have dinner yet, did you?

09:55.845 --> 09:58.264
Eat this with your sister.

09:59.473 --> 10:00.683
What about you?

10:00.766 --> 10:01.934
Don't mind me.

10:09.191 --> 10:10.776
Dad brought home pizza. Come out.

10:12.445 --> 10:13.654
I don't want any.

10:14.572 --> 10:15.865
Hurry up and come out.

10:22.663 --> 10:24.624
Hey, this is your favorite pizza.

10:48.564 --> 10:49.899
Take this too.

10:51.734 --> 10:53.736
-Go give it to him.
-What?

10:54.779 --> 10:56.155
Give it to him.

10:58.115 --> 10:59.992
You always make me do these things.

11:04.372 --> 11:06.624
Dad, Bom asked me to bring you this.

11:06.707 --> 11:08.250
Gosh, I said it's okay.

11:09.669 --> 11:10.836
Enjoy.

11:14.256 --> 11:15.549
Come and eat.

11:16.133 --> 11:17.593
-Are you going to eat here?
-Yes.

11:31.065 --> 11:33.234
-Grandma is in danger!
-Hey, stop it!

11:34.360 --> 11:36.028
Grandma is hurt!

11:36.112 --> 11:37.947
Run!

12:18.279 --> 12:19.321
Yeo-reum.

12:22.783 --> 12:24.118
I didn't know you were there.

12:25.536 --> 12:27.663
I thought you went to the library.

12:32.084 --> 12:33.461
I couldn't sleep.

12:35.087 --> 12:36.130
Same.

12:38.174 --> 12:39.341
You should sit.

12:40.050 --> 12:41.051
Okay.

12:50.144 --> 12:51.353
It's quiet here.

12:54.482 --> 12:56.859
I never thought I'd visit here.

12:58.027 --> 12:59.111
Same.

13:01.739 --> 13:03.574
It's hard to fall asleep, right?

13:05.993 --> 13:09.413
Geun-ho has been weighing on my mind.

13:09.497 --> 13:11.665
At the station earlier,

13:11.749 --> 13:14.418
Geun-ho didn't recognize me at first.

13:15.669 --> 13:17.671
It's hard to believe

13:18.297 --> 13:21.425
that someone with such a bad vision
drew graffiti and murdered someone.

13:22.843 --> 13:24.845
It's been weighing on my mind.

13:27.264 --> 13:29.725
You didn't know
that she was coming to your house

13:30.518 --> 13:31.727
around that time, right?

13:33.354 --> 13:34.396
No.

13:38.734 --> 13:40.069
Yeo-reum.

13:42.154 --> 13:44.114
Let's go to the billiard club tomorrow.

13:44.198 --> 13:46.450
No. That place…

13:47.284 --> 13:49.453
I can go alone.

13:57.419 --> 13:58.546
Dae-bum.

13:59.964 --> 14:03.008
SEON-A BILLIARD CLUB

14:20.109 --> 14:21.610
GO AWAY

14:21.694 --> 14:23.237
DIE

14:32.329 --> 14:35.916
DIE. GO AWAY, GHOST.

15:34.433 --> 15:36.852
DIE, GHOST.
YOU WHORE.

16:03.754 --> 16:05.839
Let's not stay here. Let's go.

16:11.720 --> 16:12.805
Dae-bum.

16:14.181 --> 16:15.349
It's okay.

16:18.978 --> 16:21.981
GO AWAY

16:24.149 --> 16:25.526
I'm okay.

16:25.609 --> 16:29.071
DIE, CRAZY BITCH
SLUT

16:29.154 --> 16:31.031
These graffiti.

16:31.615 --> 16:33.784
They are painted too clearly

16:34.368 --> 16:36.745
for Geun-ho to draw without glasses.

16:41.083 --> 16:43.168
I think someone is impersonating Geun-ho.

16:44.211 --> 16:46.296
But why would they murder Ms. Jung?

16:55.931 --> 16:58.100
What if someone wanted to hurt you…

17:01.687 --> 17:03.939
and frame Geun-ho for it?

17:07.109 --> 17:08.193
Geun-ho?

17:13.073 --> 17:14.825
What if Ms. Jung came in

17:15.617 --> 17:17.453
instead of you?

17:18.078 --> 17:19.371
Yeo-reum.

17:25.127 --> 17:26.295
Is that you, Geun-ho?

17:27.588 --> 17:28.714
Grandma.

17:29.423 --> 17:31.091
Hey there, Geun-ho.

17:31.175 --> 17:32.551
Ma'am.

17:32.634 --> 17:33.761
What?

17:33.844 --> 17:34.928
Run away!

17:35.012 --> 17:36.055
Geun-ho!

17:36.138 --> 17:38.307
Oh, no!

17:38.390 --> 17:39.600
Then maybe…

17:40.517 --> 17:43.270
there is more than one culprit.

17:47.149 --> 17:50.027
Geun-ho!

17:50.110 --> 17:52.279
When I saw Geun-ho last time,

17:53.280 --> 17:55.741
even a police officer couldn't
keep him under control.

18:03.749 --> 18:05.584
But who…

18:07.544 --> 18:08.921
and why?

18:12.966 --> 18:14.009
You're here.

18:15.886 --> 18:17.304
Hello.

18:21.141 --> 18:23.227
Dae-bum, what brings you here?

18:23.894 --> 18:24.853
Hello.

18:25.938 --> 18:27.981
I thought you were leaving town.

18:30.943 --> 18:31.944
No.

18:32.778 --> 18:36.657
Gosh, this is a bit awkward.

18:37.950 --> 18:39.326
Actually,

18:40.994 --> 18:44.206
I ended up becoming
the owner of this building.

18:44.790 --> 18:48.544
I'm sorry to say this,
but you'll have to move out of here.

18:53.507 --> 18:55.759
I'll give you back the rent money.

18:56.385 --> 19:00.806
Or I can find you another home in the area

19:00.889 --> 19:03.809
that's cheaper and better.

19:04.685 --> 19:05.811
Okay?

19:07.688 --> 19:09.606
So how have you been, Dae-bum?

19:10.190 --> 19:11.441
I've been okay.

19:18.073 --> 19:19.032
Ji-yeong.

19:19.116 --> 19:23.162
I haven't seen Dae-bum around
since yesterday.

19:23.245 --> 19:24.830
Do you know where he is?

19:24.913 --> 19:27.416
-Dae-bum went to Angok.
-Angok?

19:28.208 --> 19:29.793
Gosh, this bastard.

19:31.003 --> 19:32.880
Did he go there to see another movie?

19:33.881 --> 19:34.882
Did he?

19:36.592 --> 19:37.676
Professor.

19:38.302 --> 19:39.970
Dae-bum won't be returning.

19:41.221 --> 19:43.974
And I'm going to tell him the truth.

19:45.017 --> 19:45.976
The truth?

19:46.768 --> 19:47.936
What truth?

19:49.938 --> 19:51.148
Professor.

19:51.231 --> 19:54.234
I really want Dae-bum
to get back into academia again.

19:54.318 --> 19:58.447
But I don't want him
to be manipulated into researching.

19:58.530 --> 20:01.200
I want him to study of his own free will.

20:01.825 --> 20:04.286
Look here, Ji-yeong.

20:04.786 --> 20:07.372
Ahn Dae-bum and Holland
are competing with each other.

20:07.456 --> 20:09.416
Do you know what that means?

20:09.958 --> 20:11.210
But Professor Lee,

20:11.877 --> 20:16.506
Aren't you ashamed of
letting a country boy carry you?

20:20.385 --> 20:23.847
If you don't have what it takes,
you should stop being ambitious.

20:23.931 --> 20:25.307
It'll be good for you. Believe me.

20:26.183 --> 20:27.309
I'll get going.

20:37.736 --> 20:38.779
You!

20:42.532 --> 20:43.450
Gosh.

20:43.533 --> 20:46.662
Hello, come in.

20:47.579 --> 20:48.872
Come in, Dae-bum.

20:54.086 --> 20:55.754
Thank you for coming.

20:56.463 --> 20:58.548
But what brings you here?

20:59.091 --> 21:01.635
We had something to ask you.

21:02.219 --> 21:04.304
-Sure.
-Do you know

21:04.388 --> 21:08.600
why Geun-ho wasn't
wearing his glasses on that day?

21:11.561 --> 21:12.646
Glasses?

21:14.731 --> 21:16.149
A few days before the incident,

21:16.984 --> 21:20.570
he went outside and lost his glasses.

21:22.531 --> 21:24.449
We should have gotten him a new pair.

21:26.493 --> 21:29.079
Geun-ho's vision is really bad, right?

21:30.205 --> 21:31.748
It's not just bad, it's impaired.

21:32.541 --> 21:33.917
He has bad astigmatism.

21:34.001 --> 21:36.628
He can't even walk straight
without his glasses.

21:38.297 --> 21:39.798
I told you.

21:39.881 --> 21:42.467
How could a person like that
paint graffiti?

21:44.219 --> 21:48.140
Do any other people know about
the graffiti Geun-ho painted

21:48.932 --> 21:50.684
in the billiard club before?

21:52.978 --> 21:54.730
Why would we tell someone else that?

21:54.813 --> 21:57.733
If someone knew,
Mr. Bae will end up finding out.

21:58.900 --> 22:01.945
And I'm sure Geun-ho didn't do anything

22:02.821 --> 22:04.406
to make enemies, right?

22:04.489 --> 22:05.574
Enemies?

22:06.283 --> 22:10.078
All he does is draw in his room all day.

22:10.662 --> 22:12.331
There's no way he had enemies.

22:14.082 --> 22:17.252
The graffiti in the billiard club
wasn't my son's doing.

22:17.836 --> 22:21.423
He doesn't even know the obscene words
that are painted on the walls.

22:22.007 --> 22:24.384
Look what he drew on the walls.

22:25.677 --> 22:27.095
It's really not him.

22:28.180 --> 22:29.473
My goodness.

22:31.600 --> 22:34.061
Stop crying. We have guests.

22:36.188 --> 22:38.273
I'm crying because I'm so frustrated.

22:39.566 --> 22:42.819
They don't even try to listen
because he can't express himself.

22:43.320 --> 22:45.197
How can I stay calm

22:45.280 --> 22:47.949
when our son is behind bars
being forced to talk?

22:50.327 --> 22:51.495
Dae-bum.

22:51.578 --> 22:53.747
See for yourself.

22:53.830 --> 22:56.041
See if my son is capable
of writing such vulgar words.

23:11.223 --> 23:12.307
SEON-A

23:12.390 --> 23:13.975
RUN AWAY

23:14.059 --> 23:16.686
RUN AWAY SEON-A

23:24.402 --> 23:28.281
SEON-A RUN AWAY

23:28.365 --> 23:29.616
May I ask…

23:31.910 --> 23:34.204
what these letters mean?

23:36.373 --> 23:39.918
We're not sure, but he's been writing
that since when he was little.

23:41.128 --> 23:43.296
When kids like him
get hooked on something,

23:43.839 --> 23:46.007
they tend to write
and say them repeatedly.

23:46.800 --> 23:49.177
I'm sure it's meaningless.
He just draws them.

23:49.761 --> 23:52.556
Do you mind if I take a photo of this?

23:52.639 --> 23:53.598
Sure.

23:54.182 --> 23:55.183
Go ahead.

24:07.904 --> 24:09.364
Geun-ho.

24:09.447 --> 24:11.158
Look at me. Here.

24:11.825 --> 24:13.034
I got you new glasses.

24:14.119 --> 24:16.663
It must've been so frustrating.

24:16.746 --> 24:19.124
We didn't steal it, okay?

24:19.207 --> 24:20.500
We just borrowed it.

24:22.043 --> 24:23.587
Didn't you have a question for him?

24:26.715 --> 24:27.632
Hey.

24:27.716 --> 24:30.719
Put your phone down
before I confiscate it.

24:31.636 --> 24:32.721
Hey,

24:32.804 --> 24:33.889
Geun-ho.

24:38.602 --> 24:40.228
What does this mean?

24:46.109 --> 24:47.152
Geun-ho.

24:48.153 --> 24:51.156
Could you tell us what this is?

24:53.116 --> 24:54.159
Please?

24:57.287 --> 24:58.455
It's okay, Geun-ho.

24:58.538 --> 25:00.707
You can tell him, it's okay.

25:01.291 --> 25:04.002
I heard you've written this
since when you were little.

25:04.085 --> 25:05.462
What does it mean?

25:06.171 --> 25:07.422
Geun-ho, what's wrong?

25:07.505 --> 25:08.924
Calm down. It's okay.

25:09.007 --> 25:10.133
You can tell them.

25:10.717 --> 25:12.510
Then why did you write

25:12.594 --> 25:14.888
"run away" and "you'll die" on the wall?

25:14.971 --> 25:16.181
Geun-ho!

25:16.765 --> 25:18.099
It's okay.

25:18.183 --> 25:19.935
Calm yourself.

25:20.018 --> 25:22.187
You didn't kill her, right?

25:23.730 --> 25:24.814
It's okay.

25:25.440 --> 25:26.775
Are you okay, Geun-ho?

25:26.858 --> 25:28.652
You'll be okay.

25:28.735 --> 25:30.362
Look at that guy.

25:30.445 --> 25:32.364
-Look at him.
-I'm sorry.

25:32.447 --> 25:34.407
You'll be all right.

25:34.491 --> 25:37.244
It's fine, Geun-ho. I apologize for this.

25:38.870 --> 25:40.830
What are you doing this weekend?

25:41.373 --> 25:44.501
-I don't know.
-Then let's hang out all day.

25:44.584 --> 25:46.628
I'll have the day all planned out.

25:48.463 --> 25:50.840
I'm so jealous that
you can smile so happily.

25:50.924 --> 25:51.967
Me?

25:53.176 --> 25:55.053
That's not true. I have a lot on my mind.

25:56.346 --> 25:57.722
You have a lot on your mind?

25:59.641 --> 26:02.477
I'll have a lot of worries
for you on that day,

26:02.560 --> 26:03.853
so be a good listener, okay?

26:05.730 --> 26:06.815
Really?

26:07.691 --> 26:08.900
Then let's meet tomorrow.

26:09.818 --> 26:11.111
Don't you have work tomorrow?

26:11.194 --> 26:12.362
They want me to take a day off.

26:13.405 --> 26:15.365
And it's my treat tomorrow.

26:15.448 --> 26:17.325
It's fine. It's my treat.

26:17.409 --> 26:18.952
You don't even make that much.

26:20.078 --> 26:21.454
What I mean is…

26:22.122 --> 26:23.415
It's…

26:24.749 --> 26:27.002
just that I don't want to use the money

26:27.085 --> 26:29.713
-you worked so hard to make.
-Forget it.

26:29.796 --> 26:31.089
Whatever.

26:31.798 --> 26:34.301
This is part of your charm anyway.

26:36.261 --> 26:37.387
Really?

26:38.096 --> 26:39.639
It's my charm?

26:39.723 --> 26:41.433
What other charms do I have?

26:42.017 --> 26:43.351
That's enough.

26:48.064 --> 26:49.190
What did they say

26:50.692 --> 26:53.862
was the first graffiti Geun-ho painted?

26:58.158 --> 26:59.617
The first one was,

27:01.328 --> 27:03.288
"Run away, you'll die."

27:06.958 --> 27:09.586
RUN AWAY…

27:10.170 --> 27:11.212
And then?

27:12.297 --> 27:13.465
The second one was

27:14.466 --> 27:16.384
"Kill Seon-a,

27:17.052 --> 27:18.428
you saw it."

27:18.511 --> 27:19.721
YOU SAW…

27:21.473 --> 27:22.640
I'm sorry.

27:25.602 --> 27:26.853
It's okay.

27:30.190 --> 27:32.609
RUN AWAY, YOU'LL DIE
KILL SEON-A, YOU SAW IT

27:37.405 --> 27:39.324
SEON-A

27:39.407 --> 27:42.202
Do you think they're somehow connected?

27:44.037 --> 27:45.455
I'm not sure.

27:48.458 --> 27:51.336
I'm not sure if I should say this,

27:52.962 --> 27:55.131
but I heard from Geun-ho's mom

27:56.091 --> 28:01.096
that he used to like your sister, Seon-a.

28:04.140 --> 28:07.268
Ever since your sister passed,

28:07.352 --> 28:09.562
he started drawing these things.

28:11.523 --> 28:14.317
She said Geun-ho is telling me to run away

28:14.401 --> 28:17.153
because he thinks I'm her.

28:18.655 --> 28:20.448
He keeps telling me

28:21.116 --> 28:23.410
to run away by drawing these words.

28:23.493 --> 28:26.454
It really sounds like
he's telling me to run away from someone.

28:31.501 --> 28:34.045
SEON-A

28:35.004 --> 28:36.089
This…

28:37.549 --> 28:38.591
What is it?

28:39.092 --> 28:41.845
SEON-A

28:41.928 --> 28:44.431
-Look at him.
-I'm sorry.

28:44.514 --> 28:46.558
You'll be all right.

28:56.151 --> 28:57.235
Eat some rice too.

29:02.323 --> 29:03.533
Ji-yeong.

29:04.242 --> 29:05.952
What are you doing here?

29:06.536 --> 29:08.079
Hey, it's food.

29:08.163 --> 29:09.456
Good. I'm hungry.

29:11.040 --> 29:13.585
There isn't much to eat though. Hold on.

29:14.586 --> 29:15.795
Where's the spoon?

29:16.379 --> 29:17.714
It's right here.

29:19.549 --> 29:20.508
Jun.

29:20.592 --> 29:21.926
You're not even saying hi?

29:23.678 --> 29:25.805
But we're not that close.

29:28.600 --> 29:29.809
Is this too big for you?

29:30.477 --> 29:33.229
You should still say hello.
She even bought you the jacket.

29:33.313 --> 29:35.023
-Here's your spoon.
-Thank you.

29:35.106 --> 29:36.900
Thank you for accepting my gift.

29:37.400 --> 29:39.944
How come you came back
without even calling?

29:41.154 --> 29:42.238
Me?

29:44.491 --> 29:46.242
I missed Angok.

29:47.243 --> 29:48.244
What?

29:48.995 --> 29:50.622
The human heart is so strange.

29:51.664 --> 29:52.707
What do you mean?

29:52.791 --> 29:55.710
When I used to live here,
I couldn't wait to leave this place.

29:56.669 --> 29:58.296
But after a few days in Seoul,
I missed Angok.

29:59.881 --> 30:02.300
You and your fickle heart.

30:04.844 --> 30:05.845
Seong-man.

30:06.346 --> 30:08.014
Should I not go to Seoul?

30:10.850 --> 30:11.976
I mean,

30:13.603 --> 30:16.773
staying here doesn't sound too bad.

30:16.856 --> 30:17.899
Don't you think so?

30:22.195 --> 30:23.112
Hey,

30:23.196 --> 30:25.073
but it's only been a few days.

30:26.074 --> 30:28.660
Once you get busy over there,
you'll soon forget this place.

30:30.578 --> 30:32.247
Do you want me to live in Seoul?

30:37.460 --> 30:38.419
What is this?

30:38.503 --> 30:40.713
Can you talk about
these kinds of things outside?

30:41.464 --> 30:43.341
It's not like that, Jun.

30:43.967 --> 30:44.884
Don't get the wrong idea.

30:44.968 --> 30:46.094
Look.

30:46.177 --> 30:48.388
Don't do something you'll regret.

30:48.471 --> 30:50.682
You tried so hard to pass that exam.

30:51.850 --> 30:52.934
You should go to Seoul.

30:53.017 --> 30:54.686
With you gone,

30:55.645 --> 30:58.064
there's one less person
to chew my ears off.

30:58.147 --> 30:59.524
You don't mean that.

31:00.859 --> 31:01.943
You little…

31:07.198 --> 31:08.241
Hello?

31:09.450 --> 31:10.326
What?

31:11.828 --> 31:13.955
Can't my dad go instead?

31:14.581 --> 31:17.000
Okay. All right.

31:19.252 --> 31:20.753
What's wrong?

31:22.005 --> 31:25.300
This is just terrible timing.

31:25.383 --> 31:29.178
Enjoy your food, I'll be right back.

31:31.556 --> 31:33.766
-Listen to Ji-yeong, okay?
-Okay.

31:36.686 --> 31:39.022
Look at this.

31:39.105 --> 31:42.817
Do you think my kid painted this?

31:42.901 --> 31:45.028
My kid who is in jail at the station?

31:45.570 --> 31:47.864
I told you it wasn't Geun-ho.

31:47.947 --> 31:49.073
Why didn't you believe me?

31:49.157 --> 31:51.117
Of course I believe you.

31:51.200 --> 31:52.201
I mean it.

31:52.285 --> 31:53.870
And Mu-cheol!

31:54.495 --> 31:56.414
Go and tell the people at the station.

31:56.497 --> 31:58.041
I'll report it right away.

31:59.042 --> 32:01.836
And release Geun-ho immediately.

32:01.920 --> 32:03.129
Yes.

32:03.212 --> 32:04.631
But still,

32:04.714 --> 32:06.883
the footage showed him
entering this building.

32:06.966 --> 32:08.551
So we have to look into that.

32:08.635 --> 32:11.387
-So for now--
-Look into what?

32:11.471 --> 32:15.475
But what does this mean?

32:15.558 --> 32:16.768
There are two triangles,

32:17.810 --> 32:19.479
and this part looks like
some sort of letters.

32:19.562 --> 32:20.980
It is like a code?

32:23.066 --> 32:24.067
Hello.

32:24.943 --> 32:26.861
-Hello.
-Hello.

32:27.403 --> 32:28.821
Yeo-reum.

32:28.905 --> 32:31.741
What do we do?
Someone drew another graffiti here.

32:33.910 --> 32:37.163
Maybe Dad's right.
The building must be cursed or something.

32:37.872 --> 32:40.792
Hey, Mu-cheol. That security camera.

32:40.875 --> 32:42.710
Do you think it caught something?

32:43.336 --> 32:44.587
Right, check the CCTV.

32:44.671 --> 32:46.631
-Okay.
-Let's see.

32:46.714 --> 32:49.008
-Come on.
-You should've shown us first thing.

32:49.592 --> 32:50.760
Okay.

32:54.973 --> 32:56.891
There's someone there.

32:56.975 --> 33:00.228
How can you tell who this is
with this footage?

33:00.311 --> 33:02.730
Do you not have their front side?

33:02.814 --> 33:06.609
The camera is shooting from above,
so we didn't get the face.

33:06.693 --> 33:08.111
Can you not zoom in?

33:10.321 --> 33:11.406
Gosh.

33:15.410 --> 33:18.454
You get a hang of erasing this
after a couple of times.

33:20.289 --> 33:21.207
I'm sorry.

33:21.708 --> 33:24.210
What? Why are you sorry?

33:26.796 --> 33:28.256
Oh, right.

33:29.007 --> 33:31.300
You're going to have
to look for another place

33:31.384 --> 33:34.095
because this building might get sold.

33:35.138 --> 33:36.931
-Yes, I heard.
-Really?

33:37.515 --> 33:38.891
You heard already?

33:39.809 --> 33:43.187
Is it okay if I ask you a question?

33:44.230 --> 33:45.148
Go ahead.

33:52.405 --> 33:53.281
Goodbye.

33:56.409 --> 33:58.286
Hey, Lim Dae-ho.

34:00.455 --> 34:01.831
Did they turn you into a baker

34:01.914 --> 34:03.124
in juvie or something?

34:15.720 --> 34:17.263
I want to hang out every day.

34:17.764 --> 34:21.059
We can do that. Let's do this every day.

34:21.142 --> 34:24.020
Hey, get yourself together.
We're in our senior year now.

34:25.772 --> 34:27.482
Yes, ma'am.

34:29.567 --> 34:30.985
Didn't you want to talk
about your worries?

34:31.486 --> 34:32.528
What is it?

34:35.865 --> 34:37.075
Tell me.

34:38.409 --> 34:39.786
It took care of itself.

34:40.870 --> 34:42.038
That's dumb.

34:43.998 --> 34:45.708
-Stop it.
-Eat it, come on.

34:47.502 --> 34:49.295
Darn it. Now I have to go to the bathroom.

34:49.378 --> 34:51.756
-Eat this and go.
-You eat it.

35:05.103 --> 35:07.021
You insolent motherfucker.

35:07.522 --> 35:10.691
You should've come to say hello
after you were released.

35:11.275 --> 35:12.527
Do we have to go look for you?

35:14.570 --> 35:15.655
Did you just laugh?

35:16.280 --> 35:17.323
Just leave.

35:17.406 --> 35:20.243
Don't bother me
unless you're going to pay me.

35:20.326 --> 35:24.122
Do you think you're all that
because you can fight, you little shit?

35:24.622 --> 35:25.456
Hey.

35:25.540 --> 35:27.041
Do you know who we are?

35:29.210 --> 35:31.045
Is that a line they teach you

35:31.129 --> 35:32.964
at bully school?

35:33.047 --> 35:34.257
You motherfucker.

35:35.675 --> 35:36.676
And you.

35:37.176 --> 35:39.595
Stop spreading rumors about Bom.

35:40.388 --> 35:41.389
Please.

35:41.472 --> 35:43.099
Look at this punk.

35:43.683 --> 35:45.017
Is that a threat?

35:45.101 --> 35:48.104
What do you mean, a threat? I said please.

35:48.187 --> 35:49.897
"Please", my ass.

35:54.402 --> 35:56.445
You think you're better than us,
you son of a bitch?

35:56.529 --> 35:58.114
Dae-ho.

35:58.197 --> 35:59.574
Ha-neul, it's okay.

35:59.657 --> 36:01.742
-Please don't fight.
-It's fine.

36:01.826 --> 36:03.244
I'm not a kid anymore.

36:03.327 --> 36:04.912
-Go take Ha-neul.
-Come with me, Dae-ho.

36:04.996 --> 36:05.872
Come with me.

36:05.955 --> 36:07.081
Let's go, Ha-neul.

36:07.165 --> 36:08.124
Hey!

36:08.624 --> 36:09.792
-I'll talk to them and go.
-Let's just go.

36:09.876 --> 36:11.127
Come here.

36:11.711 --> 36:13.504
I'll stand still.

36:14.130 --> 36:17.008
Just hit me a few times and leave, okay?

36:20.553 --> 36:21.554
Bom.

36:31.063 --> 36:33.608
Jae-hun, I think I have to go now.

36:33.691 --> 36:36.068
-Where?
-I'll tell you later, bye.

36:36.152 --> 36:37.820
Bom.

36:37.904 --> 36:39.947
Drunks' kids are all the same.

36:40.031 --> 36:41.282
These poor fuckers.

36:41.365 --> 36:43.326
They're so busy leeching off people.

36:45.203 --> 36:46.495
You're right!

36:46.579 --> 36:48.873
Look at Bom leeching off the American boy.

36:51.083 --> 36:52.752
Take back what you just said,
and I'll let you go.

36:53.419 --> 36:54.795
What the hell are you--

36:59.592 --> 37:01.761
Wait. I have something to say.

37:01.844 --> 37:03.429
Jae-hun, I don't have time.

37:03.512 --> 37:04.972
Let's do this later, okay?

37:05.056 --> 37:06.724
Why am I always put on the back burner?

37:07.683 --> 37:09.310
You're going to Dae-ho again, right?

37:10.436 --> 37:11.354
What?

37:11.938 --> 37:14.482
You did that last time
when we were supposed to have lunch.

37:15.524 --> 37:17.318
You were with Dae-ho that day.

37:17.944 --> 37:20.780
I saw you leaving with Dae-ho
on his motorcycle.

37:22.448 --> 37:24.450
You should've told me
when you saw me then.

37:24.533 --> 37:26.452
Why are you making me look bad
after all this time?

37:26.535 --> 37:28.454
I called you,
but you said something came up.

37:28.537 --> 37:31.165
Do you want me to explain
every little detail to you?

37:32.833 --> 37:34.126
Don't go today.

37:37.004 --> 37:38.422
Jae-hun, I'm really sorry.

37:38.506 --> 37:41.175
I'll explain everything later.
This is urgent.

37:41.717 --> 37:43.469
I'm all Dae-ho has.

37:44.303 --> 37:46.681
-What?
-If Dae-ho gets in trouble again,

37:46.764 --> 37:48.432
his life is over.

37:48.516 --> 37:50.017
You're the only one for me too.

37:52.561 --> 37:54.146
I might go back to the US.

37:54.772 --> 37:55.690
What?

37:56.440 --> 37:58.734
Why are you telling me this now?

37:59.235 --> 38:01.445
Are you doing this on purpose?

38:02.822 --> 38:05.074
Fine. We can talk about that tomorrow.

38:05.157 --> 38:07.326
That's a country you can come back from.

38:07.410 --> 38:08.286
I'll get going.

38:09.245 --> 38:11.247
Hey, I told you this is urgent!

38:11.330 --> 38:13.374
You don't even know anything.

38:13.457 --> 38:15.042
You have parents to rely on

38:15.126 --> 38:16.794
but we don't!

38:16.877 --> 38:18.379
You know my story.

38:19.171 --> 38:20.673
Why would you say that?

38:21.257 --> 38:22.591
Life isn't easy for me either.

38:23.134 --> 38:24.260
Jae-hun.

38:25.219 --> 38:27.638
We are walking on thin ice every day.

38:28.222 --> 38:30.933
One wrong step can be the end for us.

38:32.018 --> 38:34.020
Why are you referring
to you and Dae-ho as "we"?

38:36.105 --> 38:37.773
Because we're different from you.

38:39.608 --> 38:43.529
Do you know how little I felt
when I visited your house?

38:43.612 --> 38:47.158
You have no idea how it hurts my pride
when you pay for everything.

38:48.367 --> 38:49.368
Then…

38:49.910 --> 38:51.495
What am I supposed to do?

38:53.456 --> 38:55.666
I know I'm the only one who likes you.

38:55.750 --> 38:56.917
I know that.

38:57.626 --> 38:59.920
But you sidelining me every single time,

39:00.004 --> 39:01.505
I can't take it anymore.

39:04.884 --> 39:06.177
You deal with that yourself.

39:07.219 --> 39:08.971
I never asked you to like me.

39:17.813 --> 39:19.774
-Hey, let's run.
-Go.

39:23.402 --> 39:24.779
Dae-ho!

39:24.862 --> 39:26.614
Let's hold back, Dae-ho.

39:27.448 --> 39:29.075
You son of a bitch!

39:33.412 --> 39:34.413
You fucker.

39:35.998 --> 39:37.291
Dae-ho!

39:37.375 --> 39:38.626
Dae-ho, please!

39:47.009 --> 39:48.177
Oh, no!

39:48.803 --> 39:49.804
Hey!

39:49.887 --> 39:51.889
-Stop it!
-Fuck!

39:52.848 --> 39:53.933
Gosh!

39:54.642 --> 39:55.976
-Come here.
-Let go.

39:56.060 --> 39:58.646
I told you to let go!

40:00.439 --> 40:01.649
You little bitch!

40:08.531 --> 40:10.825
Hey, Dae-ho!

40:11.700 --> 40:13.077
What are you doing?

40:13.160 --> 40:14.370
Move.

40:14.453 --> 40:15.746
I told you to move!

40:15.830 --> 40:17.331
Get yourself together!

40:20.418 --> 40:21.710
You were never here, okay?

40:26.090 --> 40:28.509
Fuck, it's the cops!

40:30.469 --> 40:32.054
Isn't it embarrassing
to get beaten up by a girl?

40:32.805 --> 40:34.598
So just tell them I beat you up.

40:36.934 --> 40:37.935
Damn it.

40:42.022 --> 40:44.817
Hey, over there. Stop it.

40:44.900 --> 40:46.277
Hey, stop.

40:46.360 --> 40:47.945
-What are you doing?
-You son of a bitch.

40:48.028 --> 40:49.613
Stay still.

40:49.697 --> 40:50.906
Let go.

40:50.990 --> 40:52.575
-Fucking let go!
-Take him.

40:52.658 --> 40:54.034
Are you okay?

40:54.118 --> 40:55.494
Stay still.

40:55.578 --> 40:57.705
-Fuck.
-Are you all right?

40:58.414 --> 40:59.915
Come here.

41:00.499 --> 41:01.750
Hurry up and get in the car.

41:20.936 --> 41:22.229
They picked the fight first.

41:22.313 --> 41:24.482
-Say something, Dae-ho.
-Come on.

41:24.565 --> 41:26.108
-Tell them.
-To the station.

41:26.192 --> 41:27.109
Dae-ho!

41:27.193 --> 41:28.277
Tell us at the station.

41:28.360 --> 41:29.987
-Why are you arresting him when--
-I get it.

41:30.070 --> 41:31.822
-Bom.
-This way.

41:31.906 --> 41:32.907
I don't regret this.

41:33.532 --> 41:35.618
I'll beat up all the bad guys from now on.

41:36.243 --> 41:37.745
You idiot.

41:37.828 --> 41:41.081
Why would you do this?

41:53.719 --> 41:54.970
I KNOW

41:55.054 --> 41:55.888
Hey.

41:56.722 --> 41:57.765
Who are you?

42:05.856 --> 42:06.899
I KNOW YOU KILLED HER

42:06.982 --> 42:07.900
Hey!

43:05.416 --> 43:06.500
There.

43:15.259 --> 43:17.428
Hey, stop right there!

43:26.770 --> 43:28.147
Who the hell are you?

43:28.814 --> 43:29.982
Show yourself.

43:54.465 --> 43:55.799
Girl from the billiard club?

43:58.510 --> 44:00.846
What do you think you're doing?

44:02.473 --> 44:03.766
I was curious.

44:04.350 --> 44:05.517
About what?

44:05.601 --> 44:08.979
About who is so interested
in Geun-ho's graffiti.

44:21.909 --> 44:24.286
SEON-A BILLIARD CLUB

44:24.370 --> 44:28.123
TRASH. GO AWAY, GHOST.

44:34.797 --> 44:35.839
Hey.

44:37.049 --> 44:38.175
You.

44:40.052 --> 44:41.512
Why did you sneak in here?

44:52.564 --> 44:53.649
Ahn Dae-bum.

44:55.567 --> 44:56.610
Was it you?

45:01.073 --> 45:02.699
You know what this is, don't you?

45:03.325 --> 45:04.785
It's Angok Middle School.

45:17.131 --> 45:18.340
KWAK

45:18.424 --> 45:22.261
MU

45:27.516 --> 45:31.228
CHEOL

45:32.187 --> 45:34.189
Kwak Mu-cheol from Angok Middle School.

45:34.857 --> 45:38.193
KWAK MU-CHEOL

45:39.570 --> 45:41.071
You killed her, didn't you?

45:43.866 --> 45:45.075
My sister.

45:57.129 --> 45:59.923
SEON-A

46:27.075 --> 46:28.410
You killed Ms. Jung

46:28.494 --> 46:29.995
to cover up for killing Seon-a!

46:30.078 --> 46:30.996
Stop talking nonsense!

46:31.079 --> 46:33.290
I said I didn't do it!

46:33.373 --> 46:35.709
-Vehicle 386, stop the car.
-Please keep going.

46:35.792 --> 46:37.461
It's over for you.

46:37.544 --> 46:39.087
I've been tricked. Just you wait.

46:39.171 --> 46:40.547
I won't let this slide.

46:40.631 --> 46:42.549
Everyone will know now

46:42.633 --> 46:44.384
that your son is a murderer!

46:44.468 --> 46:47.262
You know that secret recordings
can't be used in court, right?

46:47.346 --> 46:49.264
Please help us.

46:49.348 --> 46:50.724
Bom!

46:50.807 --> 46:52.267
I miss Grandma.

46:52.351 --> 46:53.477
I was wrong.

46:53.560 --> 46:54.811
I'm sorry.

46:54.895 --> 46:58.023
Subtitle translation by: Jea-Heon Chung
